body:
by **qeed.quan**:

<pre>Hi, this is a request for a floating point color struct defined inside image/color,
something like

type FRGBA32 struct {
R, G, B, A float32 
}

and 

type FRGBA64 struct {
R, G, B, A float64
}

this is for opengl/directx color formats, since the shaders default to using the
floating point to represent the colors, it will be nice to have a type already in the
package to use rather than defining your own.</pre>
